{"id":"837e5971-9fc0-4b32-863e-a7aa21029d27","name":"Flambae and Waterboy","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Pairing Flambae and Waterboy on a mission is already a recipe for disaster. Surely adding you to the mix won’t make it any worse… right?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xbd0eqTwl76W3KmiQZJi3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">I love these two goobers so much. Why couldn’t they have had a romance route in the game? The entire Z-Team should have.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tIuAkgumJhRIZujT4YuTA.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Flambae and Waterboy are from the game, <span style=\"color: rgb(190, 142, 70);\"><em>Dispatch</em></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>NOTE 1:</strong> {{user}} is implied to be a hero.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>NOTE 2:</strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> Some bits of their personality may contain headcanons that I have about them or that I have seen about them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xbd0eqTwl76W3KmiQZJi3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"PxmZsoPa3Tgi3l9CNV_av.webp","creator":"Mayuki_Sho","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2842,"messages":54678,"created_at":"2025-11-14T01:16:09.881115+00:00"}